  ;                                 VSYS ─► TPS62840 (U8) ─► VCC3V3
  ;                                 VSYS ─► TPS62840 (U9) ─► VCC1V8
  ;  VBAT ─► BQ29700 OVP/UVP/OCP ─► Protected VSYS
  ;  VCC3V3: nRF9160 VDD_GPIO, MAX-M10S VCC, DRV2605L
