  ; --- U4: LSM6DSOXTR — 6-Axis IMU (LGA-14, 3x2.5x0.83mm) ---
  ; I2C address: 0x6A (SDO tied to GND) or 0x6B (SDO tied to VDD)
  ; INT1/INT2: fall detection interrupt outputs (active high)
  ; Machine learning core: 4 finite-state machines for fall detection
